<TR><TD BGCOLOR=#d0d0ff><FONT FACE="Helvetica" SIZE=-1>
We want to welcome and thank you for trusting in us and using the e-mail
suite we designed for you.</P>

<P>Cronos II comes  with a number of features that makes it a very good
choice for your e-mail tasks on any platform, <B>GNU/Linux</B>, <B>GNU/HURD</B>,
<B>Unix</B>,
<B>FreeBSD</B>, <B>Mac-OS</B>,
<B>Microsoft Windows</B>, etc.</P>

<P>Cronos II @VERSION@ counts with the following features:

<UL>
<LI>HTML support;
<LI>attachments support;
<LI>IMAP support;
<LI>POP support;
<LI>APOP support;
<LI>Spool support;
<LI>Filters support;
<LI>Multiples identities and accounts support;
<LI>Higly GNOME integrated interface;
<LI>Interface editable through <B>Glade</B>.
</UL>

<P>You are the best person to tell what your needs are,
so if you have some other need from Cronos II, be sure
to contact us, that's <B>another feature of Cronos II</B>: Open
minded programmers.

